data.prayer: Father, encourage your church in Australian Capital Territory that you never forsake them.
data.verse: Those who know your name will put their trust in you, for you, Yahweh, have not forsaken those who seek you.

data.location_label: Photo from the state of Australian Capital Territory, Australia

data.prayer: Lord, please give apostles to expand the church into every neighborhood of Australian Capital Territory, Australia.
data.verse: Therefore go and make disciples of all nations, baptizing them in the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit, and teaching them to obey everything I have commanded you.

data.prayer: Lord, we pray for the believers in Australian Capital Territory, Australia to be more like Jesus in their love for friends and enemies.
data.verse: But I tell you, love your enemies and pray for those who persecute you.

data.prayer: Jesus, your return is closer than when we first believed. Please, set urgency in the hearts of the people living in the state of Australian Capital Territory.
data.verse: Besides this you know the time, that the hour has come for you to wake from sleep. For salvation is nearer to us now than when we first believed.

data.prayer: Lord, remember the Malay people. Make the Malay people a chosen race, a royal priesthood, a holy nation, a people for your own possession.
Lord, teach your Word to the people of the the state of Australian Capital Territory, so that they can follow your ways all their life.
data.verse: Teach me, Lord, the way of your decrees, that I may follow it to the end.

data.prayer: Father, your Word can be a lamp to the feet of the 177,185 people in the state of Australian Capital Territory who claim to know you, if they open it and read it today.
data.verse: your Word is a lamp to my feet and a light to my path.

data.prayer: Spirit, sanctify the 50,326 believers in Australian Capital Territory and keep them blameless until Jesus returns.
data.verse: May the God of peace himself sanctify you completely. May your whole spirit, soul, and body be preserved blameless at the coming of our Lord Jesus Christ. He who calls you is faithful, who will also do it.
